#       "created_at": "2026-04-24T10:35:12.123456"
#     }
#   ]
# }
###

## ==============================
## 5. Get Slogan by ID (Detail + Metadata)
## ==============================
# @name GetSloganDetail
GET {{baseurl}}/slogans/1
Content-Type: application/json
###

